Class AttractionPointDetection

  • Object
    • AttractionPointDetection

  • public class AttractionPointDetection
extends Object
    A class that handles the detection of attraction points in a road network from a complete dataset, following the principles of (Touya, 2010, "A Road Network Selection Process Based on Data Enrichment and Structure Detection" ).
    Author:
    GTouya
